<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-44-1245 </DOCNO><TEXT>Generation of photons in a curved space-time due to polarization of theelectron-positron vacuum is considered: R {yields} 2/sub {gamma}/. Ageneral expression for the number of photon pairs is obtained, and thelimits of its applicability are discussed.</TEXT></DOC>